Wyoming.title: U.S. Granted Utility Patents Originating in Non Metro/Micropolitan Statistical Areas in Wyoming
Wyoming.notes:
Utility patents are patents for invention. Patent origin is determined by the residence of the first-named inventor.

See Explanation of Data (https://www.uspto.gov/web/offices/ac/ido/oeip/taf/cls_cbsa/explan_cls_cbsa.htm) and Types of Patent Applications and Proceedings (https://www.uspto.gov/patents/basics/types-patent-applications/design-patent-application-guide) for more information.
